snippet.title: Dragon Ball FighterZ - XB1/PS4/PC/SWITCH - Cooler Gameplay
snippet.description:
Cooler shows up in a match for the first time! What do you think about him? Is he worth getting a seat in your top Dragon ball FighterZ team?

Cooler is going to be available by end September 2018 as a DLC for Dragon Ball FighterZ.
